%C6%A1ng-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-Si%C3%AAu/author-v6D2LCbIpae0gM4Dq3ytUA">Lương Khải Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-1G-ZjqcGwVRfA4XsdGDQhQ">Ngẫu thành kỳ 4 - 偶城其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Nh%C3%A0n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-02/poem-1eHT9uUwMooz1A2PSi3vCw">Nhàn vịnh kỳ 02 - 間詠其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/TchyA/Ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-M%E1%BA%ADu-huynh/poem-NHQufHXW5pFF7ky9VKLomw">Phỏng Nguyễn Mậu huynh</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/TchyA/author-rmU4qtCi4u806o6cjjfZWg">TchyA</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%A1i-t%E1%BB%AD-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n-di-ch%E1%BB%A9c-th%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-NJvolbIcDjypA5I_hCVmCw">Thái tử Trương xá nhân di chức thành nhục đoạn - 太子張舍人遺織成褥段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
